1. *Pametan* čovek uspeva da postigne svoje želje. (A wise man succeeds in achieving his desires.)

2. On je veoma *pametan* i zna da iskoristi svaku priliku. (He is very wise and knows how to take advantage of every opportunity.)

3. Ona je *pametna* i prihvata sve izazove. (She is wise and accepts all challenges.)

4. On je *pametno* odlučio da radi za sebe. (He wisely decided to work for himself.)

5. Njen *pametan* izbor je pomogao joj da postigne uspeh. (Her wise choice helped her to achieve success.)